00:07.257 --> 00:08.975
Very impressive, Hildur.

00:09.134 --> 00:10.807
And now look.

00:10.969 --> 00:12.971
<i>I listened
to Charlie's message.</i>

00:13.138 --> 00:15.106
<i>He says he's got
something to show me.</i>

00:15.265 --> 00:17.188
<i>- Yuri Lubimov.</i>
- Who is he, and what does he do?

00:17.351 --> 00:19.103
<i>He's the head of security
at the Russian mining town,</i>

00:19.269 --> 00:21.271
<i>Vukobejina</i>.
I'll take care of him.

00:21.438 --> 00:23.156
Got to bring them
something we can sell.

00:23.315 --> 00:24.862
- What?
- It's a surprise. Come on.

00:25.025 --> 00:27.369
