No, I haven't.

00:27.528 --> 00:29.826
<i>Billy Pettigrew wasn't
eaten by a bear.</i>

00:29.988 --> 00:32.332
<i>He was murdered.
The governor is responsible.</i>

00:32.491 --> 00:34.414
<i>Her sheriff killed them both.</i>

00:34.576 --> 00:36.453
A mercy killing, except...

00:36.620 --> 00:38.418
I don't believe a
fucking word of it.

