To new friends.

02:01.455 --> 02:02.331
Skol.
Skol.

02:05.917 --> 02:07.134
Mm!
Check this out.

02:07.294 --> 02:08.216
Mm!

02:08.377 --> 02:10.425
Wait. Come on.

02:10.589 --> 02:12.933
I've stood you enough drinks.
You can indulge me.

02:20.223 --> 02:22.146
What?

02:22.309 --> 02:26.780
You haven't
a clue, have you?

02:26.938 --> 02:29.817
And that is the
beauty of it.

02:29.983 --> 02:31.951
A million quid,

02:32.110 --> 02:33.862
and you can't see it.

02:37.449 --> 02:39.326
Your boys need
putting on the ferry.

02:39.493 --> 02:41.245
Sort yourself out.

02:44.331 --> 02:47.676
Too may people not doing
their fucking jobs around here.

02:47.834 --> 02:50.758
At least he isn't working
for his fucking wife.

02:52.881 --> 02:54.383
What was that?

02:54.549 --> 02:56.347
I said,
"At least he isn't working

02:56.510 --> 02:57.682
for his fucking wife."

02:57.844 --> 02:59.096
Shut your mouth.

03:17.948 --> 03:19.871
What's the matter
with you, old man?

03:20.033 --> 03:21.376
Get inside and shut
your fucking mouth.

03:21.535 --> 03:23.708
Shut your mouth
and get back inside.

03:23.870 --> 03:25.338
What?

03:25.497 --> 03:27.670
What do you think
you're doing, eh?

04:30.260 --> 04:40.260
<b><font color=#004F8C>Ripped By mstoll</b></font>

04:53.960 --> 04:55.837
♪♪

05:31.706 --> 05:33.583
♪♪

05:56.314 --> 05:58.191
♪♪

06:19.045 --> 06:22.015
Can we till right away?

06:22.173 --> 06:26.394
No, we have to put it together.
It will take some time.

06:28.346 --> 06:29.563
Thank you very much.

06:29.723 --> 06:30.895
You're welcome.
Thanks.

06:33.518 --> 06:35.896
Good work, everyone.

06:36.062 --> 06:37.564
Thank you so much.

06:37.731 --> 06:39.324
Really nice work.

06:42.277 --> 06:44.575
It'll take a few days
to set it up,

06:44.738 --> 06:47.708
'cause the hydraulics
need to settle.

06:47.866 --> 06:50.619
And they'll be drilling
by the weekend.

06:50.785 --> 06:52.128
Aren't you excited?

06:52.287 --> 06:54.540
Yes. Yes, I am. Yeah.

06:56.124 --> 06:58.343
This weeks been insane.

06:58.501 --> 07:00.378
You all did
everything you could,

07:00.545 --> 07:03.048
and now we can
look ahead.

07:03.214 --> 07:05.467
At our glacier hotel.

07:05.634 --> 07:08.137
At our future.

07:08.303 --> 07:10.522
All set,

07:10.680 --> 07:12.273
Governor!

07:12.432 --> 07:13.684
Yay!

07:38.416 --> 07:40.714
Is DCI Morton in his room?

07:40.877 --> 07:43.721
He went out...

07:43.880 --> 07:45.302
early.

07:45.465 --> 07:46.887
Do you know where?

07:49.427 --> 07:51.350
Did he say anything to you?

07:51.513 --> 07:53.561
Elena?

07:53.723 --> 07:55.521
I need you to answer me.

07:58.103 --> 08:01.448
Last night, I saw Morton.

08:03.483 --> 08:06.908
And he was pulling up the carpet
in his room.

08:07.070 --> 08:09.323
There's nothing there.

08:09.489 --> 08:12.493
He can't prove anything.

08:12.659 --> 08:14.536
I don't want
your protection, Dan.

08:14.703 --> 08:16.455
I don't want anything from you.

08:38.058 --> 08:40.732
Do it.

08:40.895 --> 08:43.023
You've never done this
before, have you?

08:43.188 --> 08:44.987
Give it to me.
I'll do it.

08:46.359 --> 08:48.612
All right.

08:53.158 --> 08:54.876
Hmm.

09:19.726 --> 09:21.979
So now what?

09:22.145 --> 09:23.772
You drink my blood?

09:23.938 --> 09:25.360
No.

09:26.775 --> 09:28.652
This does.

09:30.028 --> 09:32.326
Whatever you say, Tavi.

09:35.283 --> 09:37.877
It must be near the boy
when he sleeps,

09:38.036 --> 09:39.583
when his soul
is unprotected.

09:39.746 --> 09:42.875
Like a dream catcher.

09:43.041 --> 09:44.759
No. Not really.

09:44.918 --> 09:46.716
Listen, Henry.

09:46.878 --> 09:50.803
They say that a tupilaq can come
back to hurt the sender

09:50.965 --> 09:53.593
if what it's fighting
is too strong.

09:54.928 --> 09:57.272
Not with this.

09:59.057 --> 10:01.105
Hmm.

10:42.725 --> 10:45.023
So, you are ready to go?

10:45.186 --> 10:47.905
I had to sign papers.

10:48.064 --> 10:50.317
I won't be getting him
back for weeks, it seems.

10:50.483 --> 10:51.700
I'll push them.

10:51.860 --> 10:53.328
I'd appreciate that.

10:53.486 --> 10:55.614
I'll do anything to help you.

10:55.780 --> 10:57.532
I just want to get
out of this place.

10:59.075 --> 11:00.418
Good-bye, Hildur.

11:05.456 --> 11:07.800
I took his message
off your phone.

11:12.088 --> 11:13.965
I thought Charlie
was getting me into trouble

11:14.132 --> 11:17.306
with the glacier hotel.

11:17.468 --> 11:19.015
I'm sorry, Trish.

11:21.014 --> 11:22.766
Is this supposed
to make everything okay?

11:22.932 --> 11:25.310
He was my good friend.

11:25.476 --> 11:26.568
And me?

11:27.896 --> 11:30.524
You know,
we all lost him.

11:30.690 --> 11:35.491
I'd really like you to
know that before you go.

11:38.531 --> 11:42.377
Eric and I last fucked
two weeks ago.

11:42.535 --> 11:45.584
We've been involved
since the Solstice Party.

11:47.832 --> 11:50.130
That's not true.

11:51.961 --> 11:54.214
Those weekends
he pulled double shifts?

11:54.380 --> 11:56.553
He didn't.

11:56.716 --> 11:58.468
We were at your cabin.

11:58.635 --> 12:00.854
Charlie knew.

12:01.012 --> 12:04.232
You didn't.

12:04.390 --> 12:05.937
He's not happy.

12:06.100 --> 12:08.353
Oh, he'll never leave you.

12:08.519 --> 12:10.738
But he's not happy.

12:10.897 --> 12:13.150
He told me...

12:13.316 --> 12:16.616
so I know.

12:30.208 --> 12:33.087
♪♪

13:03.491 --> 13:05.619
You okay, Henry?

13:05.785 --> 13:09.585
A bit dizzy.

13:09.747 --> 13:11.545
You need to get
your blood sugars up.

13:11.708 --> 13:12.925
Uh...
Hobnob?

13:13.084 --> 13:15.803
No, thanks.

13:38.776 --> 13:40.653
Hello, little bird.

13:43.489 --> 13:45.742
My throat hurts.

13:47.910 --> 13:50.914
You still haven't managed
anything at all, hmm?

13:51.080 --> 13:52.047
No...

13:54.459 --> 13:56.712
Well...

13:59.297 --> 14:01.595
I've had an idea.

14:07.472 --> 14:09.895
It going to take
all the effort out of it.

14:12.101 --> 14:14.570
And this...

14:14.729 --> 14:17.448
means no dribbles.

14:17.607 --> 14:19.655
And this.

14:19.817 --> 14:21.911
A special treat.

14:22.070 --> 14:23.663
Condensed milk.

14:23.821 --> 14:25.164
Delicious

14:25.323 --> 14:28.076
and nutritious.

14:28.242 --> 14:29.915
Ah...l'm sorry.

14:30.078 --> 14:31.955
I don't feel well enough.

14:35.083 --> 14:38.303
Let's give it a go, hmm?

14:38.461 --> 14:40.338
Try a little bit.

14:40.505 --> 14:42.758
If it doesn't suit you,
then we can try something else.

14:48.721 --> 14:50.644
Hey...

14:53.017 --> 14:54.860
...you are a beautiful
little bird...

14:57.063 --> 14:58.781
...and you're gonna get
more beautiful every day.

15:43.776 --> 15:46.655
♪♪

16:14.682 --> 16:17.481
♪♪

16:25.568 --> 16:27.866
All right, there you go.

16:30.031 --> 16:32.284
Someone's had this.

16:32.450 --> 16:33.747
I checked it, darling.

16:33.910 --> 16:35.127
It's fine.

16:35.286 --> 16:37.163
You need to eat.

16:37.330 --> 16:38.582
It's calories, energy.

16:38.748 --> 16:40.250
It'll warm you up.

16:40.416 --> 16:43.169
But someone's had it already.

16:43.336 --> 16:45.088
Well... all right.

16:45.254 --> 16:47.427
There, you have that then.

16:47.590 --> 16:49.058
I don't like cheese.

16:49.217 --> 16:50.685
Well, that's why I've
given you the pie.

16:50.843 --> 16:52.095
Look, no one's

16:52.261 --> 16:54.810
eaten this bit here.
No one's touched it.

16:54.972 --> 16:56.645
You need to eat something,
Carrie, please?

16:56.807 --> 16:58.650
I don't want it.

16:58.809 --> 17:00.652
Carrie, it's food, love.

17:00.811 --> 17:02.859
Get it down you.
We're not far away now, please.

17:03.022 --> 17:04.523
Go on.

17:04.690 --> 17:07.409
Go on, get it down you.

17:07.568 --> 17:10.992
We're gonna meet
Mr. Korsky and his boat.

17:11.155 --> 17:14.829
The one who didn't
come last time?

17:14.992 --> 17:18.496
It was a misunderstanding.

17:20.373 --> 17:23.377
What if he does it again?

17:23.542 --> 17:25.136
We have these now.

17:25.294 --> 17:27.217
The tusks.

17:27.380 --> 17:30.304
When you have money,
people do what you want.

17:35.054 --> 17:38.149
Where are you going?

17:39.350 --> 17:42.354
Oh, I'm fine.

17:42.520 --> 17:43.772
Finish that pie for me.

17:43.938 --> 17:46.032
All right?
I need a wee.

18:03.374 --> 18:06.628
<i>I'm only relaying
what the mainland's saying.</i>

18:06.794 --> 18:07.795
They want him there next week.

18:07.962 --> 18:09.805
They have special facilities.

18:09.964 --> 18:11.136
And they are not in a position

18:11.299 --> 18:12.767
to assess him, only I am,

18:12.925 --> 18:15.019
and I don't think
he's capable of going

18:15.177 --> 18:17.145
anywhere next week.

18:17.305 --> 18:18.682
Hildur?

18:18.848 --> 18:20.942
Things happened
last week

18:21.100 --> 18:23.774
that were unacceptable
on a professional level.

18:23.936 --> 18:27.440
And I, too, feel bound
to air them to the mainland.

18:27.607 --> 18:30.781
What? Like what? Sheriff
Anderssen was out of control,

18:30.943 --> 18:33.412
and you covered for him.
I treated

18:33.571 --> 18:35.744
Frank Sutter after
Dan arrested him.

18:35.906 --> 18:38.375
Anywhere else but here
there would be an inquiry

18:38.534 --> 18:39.956
and he would lose his job.

18:40.119 --> 18:43.840
Oh, so y-you want Dan
to lose his job or what?

18:43.998 --> 18:46.376
That is up to the mainland
to decide, and not you

18:46.542 --> 18:51.048
and not those cozy circles
that you foster in this town.

18:51.213 --> 18:53.261
Fuck you, Margaret.

18:53.424 --> 18:56.052
You know,
fuck you and your prissy

18:56.218 --> 18:59.097
fucking bullshit.

19:01.015 --> 19:02.813
Margaret.

19:02.975 --> 19:05.228
Oops. Sorry, Doc.

19:07.188 --> 19:09.156
Is she pissed at you?

19:09.315 --> 19:11.659
I can throw her in a
cell to cool off.

19:11.817 --> 19:13.569
I can't talk...

19:13.736 --> 19:17.081
right now, Eric-- I'm busy.

19:17.239 --> 19:19.458
I'll be leaving at 6:00,

19:19.617 --> 19:22.120
to get ready for the
miners party tonight.

19:22.286 --> 19:24.789
Right.

19:44.975 --> 19:47.023
Hello, Fortitude Police.

19:47.186 --> 19:48.278
Hello?

19:48.437 --> 19:49.984
Carrie?

19:50.147 --> 19:52.400
It's Ingrid. Do you remember me?

19:52.566 --> 19:54.660
We've been worried
about you, sweetheart.

19:54.819 --> 19:58.665
My dad says we've got to leave
now, but I don't want to.

19:58.823 --> 20:00.416
I want to come home.

20:00.574 --> 20:02.167
Let me know
where you're calling from.

20:02.326 --> 20:03.828
I don't know.

20:03.994 --> 20:05.667
What the fuck?
What the fuck?

20:05.830 --> 20:08.333
What are you doing?
Hello?

20:08.499 --> 20:12.299
Ronnie? It's Ingrid,
Fortitude Police.

20:12.461 --> 20:13.963
Go and wait by the Ski-Doo.

20:16.382 --> 20:19.386
We know you didn't hurt
Professor Stoddart.

20:19.552 --> 20:20.895
Your little girl
wants to come home,

20:21.053 --> 20:22.555
and you need to
think clearly now.

20:22.722 --> 20:24.065
You need to make good decisions.

20:24.223 --> 20:25.566
I can. I do that.

20:25.725 --> 20:27.477
I make good decisions.

20:27.643 --> 20:29.486
Then bring Carrie back
to Fortitude,

20:29.645 --> 20:31.693
and we will sort this out.

20:31.856 --> 20:32.948
I give you my word.

20:33.107 --> 20:34.450
You can't give me that.

20:35.609 --> 20:37.452
So we're going.

20:37.611 --> 20:40.911
You won't stop us.
You won't take her away from me.

20:42.575 --> 20:45.624
Don't ever do that
to me again, all right?

20:45.786 --> 20:46.958
'Cause I do this for you.

20:47.121 --> 20:49.715
All of it's for you.

21:28.329 --> 21:30.627
♪♪

21:56.357 --> 21:58.655
♪♪

22:39.400 --> 22:40.401
Talking.

22:40.568 --> 22:42.445
All we'll be doing

22:42.611 --> 22:44.238
is talking.

22:46.448 --> 22:47.995
What's the matter?

22:48.158 --> 22:50.206
Do you really think I'd bring
the Fortitude cops here

22:50.369 --> 22:51.621
to back me up?

22:51.787 --> 22:55.917
This is between
you and me.

22:56.083 --> 22:59.383
So let's begin with the evidence
that you stole from my room.

23:05.009 --> 23:06.477
I said

23:06.635 --> 23:08.137
I just want to talk.

23:12.224 --> 23:13.817
You knew I'd come, didn't you?

23:13.976 --> 23:15.478
You'd thought about it.

23:15.644 --> 23:17.146
Yeah.

23:17.313 --> 23:19.031
I thought about it.

23:21.275 --> 23:23.152
So fuck you.

23:26.822 --> 23:29.496
I know who killed
Billy Pettigrew.

23:29.658 --> 23:33.162
So we'll do a deal.

23:33.329 --> 23:35.047
And I'll be keeping
what is mine.

23:35.205 --> 23:38.835
Well, we'll see about that.

23:45.841 --> 23:47.184
Henry?

23:47.343 --> 23:48.845
Dan.

23:49.011 --> 23:50.263
Would you like a drink?

23:50.429 --> 23:52.102
I'm looking for DCI Morton.

23:52.264 --> 23:53.766
He seems to have disappeared.

23:53.933 --> 23:55.856
Really?!

23:56.018 --> 23:58.612
I want you to tell me where he is.

23:58.771 --> 24:00.614
How the fuck would I know that?

24:00.773 --> 24:02.616
Because
you brought him here.

24:02.775 --> 24:05.745
What are you talking about?

24:05.903 --> 24:09.453
You used that phone,
and you called London.

24:11.575 --> 24:14.078
You told him
I murdered Stoddart.

24:14.244 --> 24:16.667
Just as I murdered Pettigrew.

24:16.830 --> 24:18.582
I told you

24:18.749 --> 24:21.252
about my feelings for Elena.

24:21.418 --> 24:22.840
I trusted you with that.

24:23.003 --> 24:25.472
The same day, Morton brings her
in for questioning.

24:25.631 --> 24:27.053
Threatens
to ruin her whole life.

24:27.216 --> 24:29.059
Just to get at me.

24:29.218 --> 24:31.266
No, that's not right.

24:31.428 --> 24:32.395
I trusted you, Henry.

24:34.223 --> 24:37.067
I let you stay on this island
so you could die well.

24:37.226 --> 24:39.274
I wanted to be there for you.

24:39.436 --> 24:42.064
So tell me,

24:42.231 --> 24:44.575
where's Morton?

24:44.733 --> 24:48.408
All I did was make the call
and nothing else.

24:48.570 --> 24:53.201
What the fuck have I done...?

24:58.122 --> 25:00.375
I don't know.

25:04.878 --> 25:06.721
<i>You didn't actually see</i>

25:06.880 --> 25:10.475
Eric Odegard put Billy Pettigrew
into the police car.

25:10.634 --> 25:12.477
I didn't have to.

25:12.636 --> 25:14.479
He disappeared.

25:14.638 --> 25:17.892
The next day they're pulling
his carcass off that beach.

25:18.058 --> 25:20.311
See, what you're giving me here

25:20.477 --> 25:22.400
is circumstantial evidence.

25:22.563 --> 25:25.112
I think I will be taking
that printout back with me.

25:45.544 --> 25:49.265
I found that on the beach
where Pettigrew was killed.

25:49.423 --> 25:53.849
The bullet came from
a .375 hunting rifle.

25:54.011 --> 25:56.480
Standard Fortitude police issue.

25:57.973 --> 26:00.977
Hmm, hmm?

26:01.143 --> 26:04.613
Do the ballistics
on Eric Odegard's rifle.

26:04.772 --> 26:07.241
That's his slug
I found on the beach.

26:09.318 --> 26:10.945
Why not another cop?

26:11.111 --> 26:13.830
Oh, they're all in it.

26:13.989 --> 26:15.957
They're all covering for Eric.

26:16.116 --> 26:17.914
Sheriff Anderssen, too?

26:18.077 --> 26:21.832
He carries around photos
of Pettigrew's body parts.

26:21.997 --> 26:23.920
He tried to scare me with them.

26:24.083 --> 26:26.336
Why would he scare you?

26:26.502 --> 26:28.379
I said he tried.

26:35.803 --> 26:37.680
I've given you plenty.

26:41.725 --> 26:43.602
You can go now.

26:49.316 --> 26:52.115
Eric killed Pettigrew

26:52.277 --> 26:54.120
for that printout, okay?

26:54.279 --> 26:55.872
But that's mine now.

26:56.031 --> 26:58.125
And I get the Fortitude police
off your back

26:58.283 --> 26:59.751
if I nail Eric, right?

26:59.910 --> 27:01.332
Sounds like a deal.

27:01.495 --> 27:02.917
Sounds like paranoia.

27:18.971 --> 27:21.474
Aren't you curious...

27:21.640 --> 27:23.893
what this is about?

27:26.061 --> 27:27.779
