33:13.992 --> 33:15.369
Plank, plank, plank, plank!

33:15.535 --> 33:16.707
Jesus, Pettie.

33:16.870 --> 33:18.793
Come on, we're
not in uniform.

33:20.373 --> 33:22.796
♪ And I've lost ♪

33:22.959 --> 33:24.927
♪ My light, for I toss
and turn... ♪

33:25.086 --> 33:26.759
So, which one?

33:26.922 --> 33:28.799
Or all three between us?

33:28.965 --> 33:31.514
No way, you're on your own.

33:31.676 --> 33:33.895
It wouldn't be
the first time.

33:36.723 --> 33:38.566
Seriously, slow down.

33:38.725 --> 33:40.147
You're freaking me out.

33:42.354 --> 33:44.448
♪ Take my tears and that's ♪

