38:15.794 --> 38:18.263
And for those of you
who are staying on

38:18.421 --> 38:20.515
to work on our new venture,

38:20.673 --> 38:23.142
you better wash off
the coal dust.

38:23.301 --> 38:26.805
Governor Odegard wants
that glacier hotel spotless.

38:26.971 --> 38:28.848
Skol!

38:29.015 --> 38:30.267
Skol!

