38:54.332 --> 38:57.677
♪ I search for the beat
in this dirty town ♪

38:57.836 --> 39:00.180
♪ Downtown the young ones... ♪

39:00.338 --> 39:03.592
If you were so unhappy,

39:03.758 --> 39:06.011
why didn't you tell me?

39:06.177 --> 39:08.179
You owe me that,
don't you think?

39:08.346 --> 39:10.644
I'm not unhappy.

39:12.225 --> 39:14.068
I just want us
to be closer.

39:14.227 --> 39:15.570
We don't spend
much time together.

39:15.728 --> 39:17.401
Oh, I'm not there for you?

39:17.564 --> 39:19.658
Is that what you're saying?
It's part of it, yeah.

39:19.816 --> 39:21.068
Your job, your plans, your...

39:21.234 --> 39:23.453
My job.

39:23.611 --> 39:26.990
So you fuck one of my best
friends because I'm busy?

39:27.156 --> 39:28.499
Hildy.

39:38.084 --> 39:40.257
I'm going to the
mainland in the morning.

39:40.420 --> 39:43.139
I don't want to see
you before I leave.

40:37.435 --> 40:39.233
Ah.

40:39.395 --> 40:41.318
Why did you go
and see my son?

40:41.481 --> 40:44.109
Relax.
What did you say to him?!

40:44.275 --> 40:48.530
Not here. Please. No. Please. Why? Because
you don't want all these people to know

40:48.696 --> 40:51.870
