because of you? Huh?

40:52.033 --> 40:53.125
Huh?

40:53.284 --> 40:54.501
No.

40:54.661 --> 40:57.039
It started because of us.

41:00.166 --> 41:01.713
Oh. Oh, oh. Oh, oh.

41:04.212 --> 41:06.510
Leave her alone, Frank.

41:08.883 --> 41:11.136
You're upset.

41:11.302 --> 41:14.021
I understand that.

41:16.182 --> 41:18.230
Go home to your wife.

42:32.550 --> 42:34.848
Can I get a drink?

42:42.935 --> 42:45.233
What were you doing?

42:45.396 --> 42:46.613
I don't know.

42:46.773 --> 42:48.696
Wanted to protect
me some more?

42:48.858 --> 42:51.452
He was going to hit you.

43:01.162 --> 43:03.460
Dan?

43:04.749 --> 43:07.002
Dan?

43:07.168 --> 43:09.421
You can't talk to me.

43:09.587 --> 43:11.589
