43:11.756 --> 43:13.884
We've never even
had a conversation.

43:15.259 --> 43:18.763
So, you don't
know who I am.

43:18.930 --> 43:21.399
I'm just an idea in your head.

43:21.557 --> 43:23.776
No.

43:23.935 --> 43:26.233
You're wrong.

43:36.239 --> 43:39.118
Okay. Then tell me what
happened to Pettigrew.

43:44.247 --> 43:46.500
I didn't kill him.

43:49.502 --> 43:52.472
You know Morton's not gonna
leave here until he's got you.

44:19.949 --> 44:22.247
